HEADWORD: Logaœdic
<hw>Log`a*⟦oe⟧d"ic</hw> <pr>(l⟦ocr⟧g`⟦adot⟧*⟦ecr⟧d"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>logaoidiko`s</grk>; <grk>lo`gos</grk>
